snippet.title: 📢 DEMO DROPS NOVEMBER 1ST 📢
snippet.description:
The GLUM demo is launching on November 1st! Finally, you'll be able to get your goblin on and enter our twisted world of mischief, mayhem and questionable life choices. 😈 🤘Remember to wishlist GLUM on Steam, so you’ll get notified when the demo drops🔥

Wishlist our game on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2235550/Glum_A_Wicked_Misadventure/
